snippet.title: Paleo Pines - Pre-Order Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Paleo Pines, a charming island known for its friendly dinosaurs, quirky townsfolk, and mysterious past. Here, evolution took a different path, creating a world in which humans and dinosaurs live together in harmony!

Set out with your dino companion, Lucky, to uncover the island’s secrets and discover new dinosaurs. Together with Lucky, build a thriving ranch, assist local villagers, befriend adorable dinosaurs, and unearth the island’s lost history to build your cozy dino sanctuary.

Coming September 26 to Steam, PlayStation 4 & 5, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch! Wishlist & preorder now at PaleoPines.com.

Follow Paleo Pines on social: 

Twitter: https://twitter.com/PaleoPines
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/paleopines/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@paleopines
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/5mjbs6D
